# NO TAILWIND CSS

This project has **MIGRATED AWAY** from Tailwind CSS. Do not suggest or generate any Tailwind patterns.

## NEVER suggest or use:

### Tailwind Color Tokens
- `text-gray-500`, `bg-slate-100`, `border-blue-600`, etc.
- Any color class with a number suffix

### Responsive Prefixes
- `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`, `xl:`, `2xl:`
- Example: `md:flex`, `lg:grid-cols-4`

### State Prefixes
- `hover:`, `focus:`, `focus-visible:`, `active:`, `disabled:`
- `group-hover:`, `group-focus:`
- `data-[state=...]` patterns in className
- Example: `hover:bg-primary`, `focus:ring-2`

### Arbitrary Values
- `bg-[#color]`, `text-[#hex]`, `border-[rgba(...)]`
- `w-[256px]`, `h-[100px]`, `min-h-[400px]`
- `text-[15px]`, `leading-[24px]`, `tracking-[0.1px]`
- `rounded-[20px]`, `rounded-[10px]`

## ALWAYS use instead:

### For Layout & Spacing
Use utility classes from `src/utilities.css`:
```tsx
className="flex items-center gap-4 p-4"
```

### For Colors
Use CSS custom properties via inline styles:
```tsx
style={{ color: 'var(--ds-text-default)', backgroundColor: 'var(--purple-magic-600)' }}
```

Or semantic classes:
```tsx
className="text-muted-foreground bg-background"
```

### For Hover/Focus/Responsive States
Define in component CSS (`src/components.css`):
```css
.my-button:hover {
  background-color: var(--purple-magic-700);
}

.my-button:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--purple-magic-600);
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .my-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
}
```

### For Border Radius
Use ONLY the 4-tier system:
- `rounded-sm` (4px) - compact elements
- `rounded-md` (8px) - **DEFAULT for most elements**
- `rounded-lg` (12px) - large containers
- `rounded-full` (9999px) - circular elements

### For Typography
Use design system classes:
```tsx
className="text-body text-title-secondary text-label-demi"
```

